  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On March 13, the whole-- No, let me-- let me come back a few days before.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Already then, when I was going into the ghetto to sleep and-- and working in Plaszow as a barackenbau, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was-- the commander of the-- of the camp was by the name Amon Goeth.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You probably know the name, because it's very known, very known name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] By him, a person was nothing, like a-- like a fly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If he saw that somebody didn't work, he took a gun and he was-- he was shot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some-- sometimes, even if somebody was working, he shot that man, how he wanted to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This Amon Goeth, he brought some people into the ghetto-- into the Plaszow, into the Plaszow, somewhere around 5,000 or 6,000 people into the Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the rest was staying in ghetto yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The ghetto wasn't liquidated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ghetto into the Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some stay a little longer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the traffic was between the ghetto and Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People from Plaszow used to go to work to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because still, in Paszow, was not-- no work to tend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no-- no factories made, only some sleeping barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And two girls didn't-- two women, girls, young girls didn't come back for one night, didn't come back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And like, you know about it, that every morning we had appells.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they count people, how many people there were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if somebody was missing, they had to look for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On one of those days, on the appell, the Jewish policemen, two Jewish policemen, who were there, in Plaszow, already, came to Goeth, because he-- always, by appell, he was present, and told them that they are missing two people.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
